snippet.title: Dead Hand Beta Teaser
snippet.description:
Dead Hand is tactical turn based roguelike game in development by One Man Army Games All footage is taken ingame from the beta version.

http://www.onemanarmygames.com/dead-hand/

Parts of the song "紅獏" by "Nanten" used under the "CC BY 2.1 JP" license: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.1/jp/deed.en
Parts of the song "illdustrial" by "Z Asmut" used under the "CC BY 3.0" license: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
